dct_description_sm: Shows international and administrative boundaries, four classes of roads and three classes of railroads. Relief shown by contours, gradient tints and spot heights. "Stand: 1930 - 41, Einzelne Nachträge 1942 Nur für den Dienstgebrauch!" "IV. 1942 (D 37)." Map surveyed 1930-41. Prepared for the use of the German Army. The roads are oveprinted. Princeton University Map Collection is missing sheets 1 and 5. Princeton University Map Collection is missing sheet 1, and 5.
dct_creator_sm: Germany. Heer. Abteilung für Kriegskarten- und Vermessungswesen II
dct_publisher_sm: [Berlin] : Generalstab des Heeres Abteilung fü̈r Kriegskarten- und Vermessungswesen (II), 1942.
dct_spatial_sm: Russia. Russian Empire. Soviet Union. Former Soviet Republics
